## **_KENNY OMEGA DEF. CHRISTIAN BLAKE_** in a fairly easy fashion

Post match Omega cuts a promo saying he will beat his opponents at Dynasty. This brings out Mike Bailey but they're both interrupted by Ricochet who says he wishes he could be at Dynamite to slap both men but he is at his wedding this week.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/42b2848c-036b-45d7-9e35-ed875b2a46cf/20250326_171809.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2c70e91c-8218-41d6-96aa-2c876fcb5fb6/20250326_172012.jpg)

Chris Jericho challenges Bandido to a Mask vs ROH World Title Match at Dynasty

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/762ced3a-cc1e-4ce7-b8dc-cb9ed10346db/20250326_172402.jpg)

MJF calls MVP out to the ring to announce that he ACCEPTS THE DEAL. MJF WANTS TO JOIN THE HURT SYNDICATE…

Bobby Lashley and Shelton Benjamin interrupt before the deal can be closed. Lashley walks up to MJF and asks for the Hurt Syndicate card. He rips it up and threatens MJF.

MVP asks Lashley to relax. MJF asks MVP what's going on. MJF backs off and says they'll talk. MVP asks Lashley what's wrong now, they've always trusted him before.

Big Bill and Bryan Kieth take this opportunity to walk out and challenge for the Tag Team Championships. But MVP tells them they would have to actually win a match as a tag team before they get a shot.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/91cdfb72-eec3-4921-bc0b-ca3e192fa15c/Screenshot_20250326_173111.jpg)

