![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4e50d490-ccff-4043-bc1a-4fbce93bb193/Screenshot_20250326_175457.jpg)

*   ## **_KYLE FLETCHER DEF. BRODY KING_**
    

Very fun match that ends when Mark Davis comes out to interfere behind the referee's back. Post match, Aussie Open start to beat down Brody King when Davis' opponent in the next match HOBBS runs out for the save

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/964e5ad5-c817-42b2-bf4f-390d3382f997/20250326_180557.jpg)

*   ## **_Powerhouse Hobbs def. Mark Davis_** in a massive hoss battle
    

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/4af52f9e-13b6-4430-9ce2-6fbf4d051a34/Screenshot_20250326_181735.jpg)

Swerve warns Hangman to stay out of his business before going out to the ring to call out Jon Moxley.

Moxley comes out and says the business has been taken over by billionaires, Hollywood agencies and kids who see the world through Instagram filters.

But Swerve gives Moxley hope. However, Mox doesn't know if Swerve has what it takes to finish him off.

Marina Shafir tries to sneak up on Swerve but Willow Nightengale runs out to stop her. Moxley decided to leave since the odds were evened out.

But not before Shafir and Willow gets into a big brawl.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e5e3fce4-2d0b-4c2d-bd66-eeb6bc479e58/Screenshot_20250326_181912.jpg)

